{"tid":2053112,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"警稱遭磚掟胸 睇片改口無擊中","createTime":"2020-06-06T04:20:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-06T12:18:28.000Z","uid":25558,"like":538,"dislike":61,"uniUserReply":131,"replies":[{"pid":"a1bd81f18cbf825ccca788759142c135052d650f","tid":2053112,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T04:20:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200606/VMQNN2LXPQXKKGQ2NBZLIV4ZDI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200606%2FVMQNN2LXPQXKKGQ2NBZLIV4ZDI%2F&d=bCxsXTpKmrqj5N4FYztdxxTmJET03dBbukdTSFliYCA%3D&h=cd5d4b32\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200606%2FVMQNN2LXPQXKKGQ2NBZLIV4ZDI%2F&h=b9dc9fff\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200606/VMQNN2LXPQXKKGQ2NBZLIV4ZDI/</a><br />\n<br />\n警稱遭磚掟胸 睇片改口無擊中<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n被告林耀庭被控襲警罪受審。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】科大生周梓樂去年11月初在將軍澳墮樓不治，市民在多區默哀悼念，其後演變為警民衝。。。。。。。。。。過傳媒影片後改稱磚塊只是擲向他的胸口，被質疑說謊。另一警員則被指在現場「求其」執一塊磚當作證物。<br />\n<br />\n無。。。。。。。。案件押後至本月24日裁決。<br />\n<br />\n魯供稱事發當晚有紀念活動，集會人士在活動結束後指罵警方稱「黑警死全家」。及後他與同袍準備登上警車，人群突靠近並向警方投擲雜物。<br />\n被指「求其」執磚作證物<br />\n<br />\n魯續稱，他看見一名穿黑衣的高大男子站在他左前方的警車旁，右。。。。。。。。。。到佢」，在軒尼詩道路面捉到被告，向被告噴胡椒噴劑，同袍則為被告戴上手銬。魯的左手中指及右手拇指擦傷。<br />\n<br />\n辯方指出，魯的證人口供紙上是寫「硬物擊中我左胸位置」，魯確認，但坦言事實上硬物並沒擊中他的左胸。辯方質疑魯只因看過有關影片，才在庭上說出另一版本。魯否認說謊。<br />\n<br />\n辯方又質疑魯追捕期間曾噴胡椒噴劑，根本望不到身處另一邊的掟。。。。。。強調「眼尾見到」，又指被告「同我距離好近」。辯方指被告並非掟磚者，只因跑。。。。。。。有份追捕的警員謝南偉供稱，在行人路尋回涉案紅磚；辯方指他只是「求其」執一塊磚，他否認。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：ESCC2509/19<br />\n■記者戴國輝<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/LLJFEOIUWHNCGKGYU524ZREMUI.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FLLJFEOIUWHNCGKGYU524ZREMUI.gif&h=d3f3b167&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n警員謝南偉否認「求其」執磚作證物。"},{"pid":"d9a8d8f101917754f19086e5402833c354ae236f","tid":2053112,"uid":335303,"like":539,"dislike":4,"score":535,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T04:22:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f1kDvQh.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff1kDvQh.gif&h=30bd7c2a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0cc10bbef9ab27b0c7252321d872aa09978f3094","tid":2053112,"uid":19126,"like":154,"dislike":2,"score":152,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T04:22:57.000Z","msg":"根本夾埋鳩砌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d0afdd265a9043eba5c4e09a6307ea5c70fa395","tid":2053112,"uid":81236,"like":562,"dislike":3,"score":559,"citedBy":13,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T04:25:15.000Z","msg":"比假口供都唔犯法？<br />\n<br />\n犯法就犯法<br />\n<br />\n除非你係香港警察<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc97cf61ae58257837c84a31540e0668073d03df","tid":2053112,"uid":158404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T04:25:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"050e9adeb6d6fc9da46826ce39cbde8740b4f8aa","tid":2053112,"uid":228868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T04:26:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"badcb8fd6d8af1c13106f6a243f4fd8966319d4e","tid":2053112,"uid":250654,"like":37,"dislike":1,"score":36,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T04:28:29.000Z","msg":"法治已死係已確認嘅事<br />\n又鞭屍<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fa0acb122cc15ccaf7d61db912b28adb05afa1c","tid":2053112,"uid":158888,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T04:28:46.000Z","msg":"不誠實証人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e93947e688738f897c980adf528187b2dca00a9","tid":2053112,"uid":297997,"like":41,"dislike":1,"score":40,"quote":{"pid":"8d0afdd265a9043eba5c4e09a6307ea5c70fa395","tid":2053112,"uid":81236,"like":562,"dislike":3,"score":559,"citedBy":13,"replyTime":"202