向被告噴胡椒噴劑，同袍則為被告戴上手銬。魯的左手中指及右手拇指擦傷。<br />\n<br />\n辯方指出，魯的證人口供紙上是寫「硬物擊中我左胸位置」，魯確認，但坦言事實上硬物並沒擊中他的左胸。辯方質疑魯只因看過有關影片，才在庭上說出另一版本。魯否認說謊。<br />\n<br />\n辯方又質疑魯追捕期間曾噴胡椒噴劑，根本望不到身處另一邊的掟。。。。。。強調「眼尾見到」，又指被告「同我距離好近」。辯方指被告並非掟磚者，只因跑。。。。。。。有份追捕的警員謝南偉供稱，在行人路尋回涉案紅磚；辯方指他只是「求其」執一塊磚，他否認。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：ESCC2509/19<br />\n■記者戴國輝<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/LLJFEOIUWHNCGKGYU524ZREMUI.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FLLJFEOIUWHNCGKGYU524ZREMUI.gif&h=d3f3b167&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n警員謝南偉否認「求其」執磚作證物。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T05:05:08.000Z","msg":"比假口供有無罪？"},{"pid":"6dc3bfc1512ee79ddaf8f6e0d83335076852713d","tid":2053112,"uid":262674,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"8d0afdd265a9043eba5c4e09a6307ea5c70fa395","tid":2053112,"uid":81236,"like":562,"dislike":3,"score":559,"citedBy":13,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T04:25:15.000Z","msg":"比假口供都唔犯法？<br />\n<br />\n犯法就犯法<br />\n<br />\n除非你係香港警察<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T05:05:37.000Z","msg":"玩私人提告得唔得？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a7f62bd6b7e9653b700489abe6c90b3c3c7c869","tid":2053112,"uid":262674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a8d4dec51ceb26e9afdf1f8e65179db676a688b2","tid":2053112,"uid":143499,"like":57,"dislike":2,"score":55,"quote":{"pid":"8d0afdd265a9043eba5c4e09a6307ea5c70fa395","tid":2053112,"uid":81236,"like":562,"dislike":3,"score":559,"citedBy":13,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T04:25:15.000Z","msg":"比假口供都唔犯法？<br />\n<br />\n犯法就犯法<br />\n<br />\n除非你係香港警察<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T04:29:22.000Z","msg":"犯法不過律政司唔肯告<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T05:05:55.000Z","msg":"私人提告"},{"pid":"e4ad0c2cd564a